{{Quote|The droid machines require nearly two tens of days to cleanse a single pirkha of land. My daughters could destroy the kholm&mdash;grass there in one.|Vor'corkh|<ref name="DFR">''[[Dark Force Rising]]''</ref>}}
A '''''pirkha''''' was a [[Noghri/Legends|Noghri]] measurement of land. [[Dynast]] [[Vor'corkh]] estimated that the slow-working [[Decon III|decon droid]]s required nearly twenty days to cleanse a single ''pirkha'' of land.

